trans-unit.source: Azure Active Directory All User Sign In Activity Report | Microsoft Azure
trans-unit.target: Azure Active Directory All User Sign In Activity Report | Microsoft Azure

trans-unit.source: A report containing all sign ins from users in your Azure Active Directory
trans-unit.target: A report containing all sign ins from users in your Azure Active Directory

trans-unit.source: Azure Active Directory All User Sign In Activity report
trans-unit.target: Azure Active Directory All User Sign In Activity report

trans-unit.source: This documentation is part of the [Azure Active Directory Reporting Guide](active-directory-reporting-guide.md).
trans-unit.target: This documentation is part of the [Azure Active Directory Reporting Guide](active-directory-reporting-guide.md).

trans-unit.source: The All User Sign In Activity report is a premium report in Private Preview.
trans-unit.target: The All User Sign In Activity report is a premium report in Private Preview.

trans-unit.source: To get access to the report, email aadreportinghelp@microsoft.com with your domain name (something like **contoso.onmicrosoft.com**)
trans-unit.target: To get access to the report, email aadreportinghelp@microsoft.com with your domain name (something like **contoso.onmicrosoft.com**)

trans-unit.source: The All User Sign In Activity report contains all sign ins from all users in your directory, including date and time, UPN, IP address, and the application that the user signed into.
trans-unit.target: The All User Sign In Activity report contains all sign ins from all users in your directory, including date and time, UPN, IP address, and the application that the user signed into.

trans-unit.source: The All User Sign In Activity report is currently only available through the Reporting API.
trans-unit.target: The All User Sign In Activity report is currently only available through the Reporting API.

trans-unit.source: Visit [Getting Started with the Reporting API](active-directory-reporting-api-getting-started.md) to learn more.
trans-unit.target: Visit [Getting Started with the Reporting API](active-directory-reporting-api-getting-started.md) to learn more.
